name: CatWalk (LoadingRemexe)
description:
Partnered With: Technatron who drew all the art. Submitted for the BlackThornProd Game Jam 3. The Game Jam Theme was "Less Is More"

So here is a cat game where you try to use as little food as possible to lure it to the end!

Outside Assets used:

  • Fonts: PUSAB by Flat-it, Messy Fika by Viktor Örneland
  • Audio SFX: CC0 from Freesound.org
  • Soundtrack: Su Turno by Patrick de Arteaga (patrickdearteaga.com)
